<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-6 col-centered">
			<a class="about-anchor" id="about"></a>
			<h1 class="text-center">About</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="col-md-8 col-centered">
			<p>Inspired by classic action JRPGs, Destiny Chronicles is an action role-playing game about a girl named Celeste who goes on a journey to prove herself worthy of becoming a true knight. Her quest will take her far from her home, across the continent in pursuit of a thief whose actions stem from a darker plan.</p>

			<p>Its character-driven plot focuses on the interactions between Celeste and her companions as they search for the thief. Our goal is to make the game lighthearted and humorous, but still tell a compelling story.</p>

			<p>Destiny Chronicles features an exciting, fast-paced action combat system similar to that of Kingdom Hearts, set in a world inspired by JRPGs. A talent tree and an upgrade system will allow you to customize Celeste’s fighting style to suit your playstyle.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
