			<h1 class="text-center">Characters</h1>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
					<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/celeste_face.png",id: "celeste-profile",class:"char-portrait img-circle") %>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
					<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/ruby_face.png",id: "ruby-profile",class:"char-portrait img-circle") %>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
					<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/valana_face.png",id: "valana-profile",class:"char-portrait img-circle") %>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
					<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/valana_face.png",id: "thief-profile",class:"char-portrait img-circle") %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div id="celeste">
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
				<h2>Celeste</h2>
				<p>Celeste grew up among the knighthood, isolated from the larger world. She always dreamed of becoming a knight herself to protect people, but things aren’t as simple as she imagined them to be.  
				</p>
				<p>
					Now, a thief has ruined her initiation, and she’s determined to prove herself. Although she knows little about the outside world, she ventures out on her own to reclaim what was stolen. 
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-5">
				<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/celeste.png",class:"char-profile-img",alt: "celeste") %>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="ruby" class="char-hidden">
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
				<h2>Ruby</h2>
				<p>Ruby is a skilled mage who has devoted her life to research. So much of the world’s past is shrouded in mystery, and she intends to be the one who learns the truth. 
				</p>
				<p>
					She’s currently searching for a shadowy organization most people believe is only a myth. Can she prove its existence? When her path crosses ways with Celeste’s, she jumps at the chance to see what truths her quest will uncover. 
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/ruby.png",class:"char-profile-img",alt: "ruby") %>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="valana" class="char-hidden">
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
				<h2>Valana</h2>
				<p>Valana is a mercenary. She has a soft spot for people in trouble and occasionally offers assistance free of charge, although she still fights monsters and hunts down criminals for pay. 
				</p>
				<p>
					When she meets Celeste, she recognizes the young knight as someone who really needs a guide to steer her away from trouble. Fortunately, they have a shared goal, although just why she’s hunting the thief is anyone’s guess.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/valana.png",class:"char-profile-img",alt: "valana") %>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="thief" class="char-hidden">
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
				<h2>Thief</h2>
				<p>Who is the mysterious woman who stole the artifact before Celeste could claim it? What does she want with it?
				</p>
				<p>
					Her path takes her far to the north, into hostile lands beyond known civilizations. Although she fights Celeste whenever their paths cross, she claims to have a noble cause. She keeps her motives to herself, but there’s more to this apparent thief than meets the eye. 
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<%= image_tag("destiny-chronicles/valana.png",class:"char-profile-img",alt: "valana") %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container" style="padding-bottom:10px;">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-6 col-centered">
			<a class="story-anchor" id="story"></a>
			<h1 class="text-center">Story</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="col-md-8 col-centered">
			<p>For centuries, an order of knights has protected the people from monsters. Celeste, a young initiate, is sent to the forest village of Village Name to prove herself worthy of knighthood by retrieving an ancient artifact that has corrupted the forest.</p>

			<p>When a mysterious young woman steals the artifact before Celeste can take it, she fails her initiation. Determined to prove herself, Celeste leaves home on her own to find the thief, reclaim the artifact, and become a knight.  </p>

			<p>But the outside world is much different than the isolated society Celeste grew up in, and she joins forces with a mercenary named Valana and a researcher named Ruby. Their journey takes them across a continent filled with mysterious ruins, remnants of an ancient civilization that crumbled ages ago. No one knows who they were or why they fell, and the stolen artifact is one of the few remaining relics from their era.</p>

			<p>The more Celeste sees of the world, the more she questions not only her mission, but also the role of the knighthood. Is it right for them to remain separate from the rest of the world? Do they protect people as much as they claim, or have they prioritized the artifacts above the lives of the people they claim to protect?</p>

			<p>One thing is certain: the woman who took the artifact is no ordinary thief, and the stolen artifact is only the tip of a dark plot. A mysterious destiny ties them together, and this journey will change Celeste’s life forever. </p>
		</div>
	</div>

